I '''Maria Yuryevna Sharapova''' ({{lang-ru|link=no|Мария Юрьевна Шарапова}} {{IPA-ru|mɐˈrʲijə ˈjurʲjɪvnə ʂɐˈrapəvə||Maria_sharapova.ogg}}; mibait April 19, 1987) metung yang [[Russia]]n a propesyonal a talapamyalung [[tennis]] player. Anyang Junio 11, 2012 maki ranggu yang [[List of WTA number 1 ranked players|world no.&nbsp;1]]. Metung yang [[Permanent residence (United States)|residenti ning Estados Unidos]] manibat anyang 1994<ref>[http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/europe/backhanded-compliments-as-russian-stars-slam-sharapova-555254.html]''The Independent'', By Andrew Osborn in Moscow, Tuesday, August 3, 2004</ref> i Sharapova, a sinambut 27 (adwang pulu't pitung) titulung [[Women's Tennis Association|WTA]] single, kayabe la reng apat a titulung [[Grand Slam (tennis)|Grand Slam]] single. Sinambut ya mu naman king [[2004 WTA Tour Championships – Singles|WTA Tour Championships in 2004]] king mapupus ning banwa. Dininan neng ranggu ning [[Women's Tennis Association]] i Sharapovang [[List of WTA number 1 ranked players|Mumuna king yatu (World No. 1)]] king singles kareng limang mikakawaning pamikatagun. Megi yang mumuna king yatu (world no. 1) king mumunang pamikatagun anyang Agosto 22, 2005, at ikwa ne king kalimang pamikatagun anyang Junio 11, 2012.<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.3news.co.nz/Maria-Sharapova-reclaims-world-number-one-ranking/tabid/415/articleID/257186/Default.aspx | title= Maria Sharapova reclaims world number one ranking| date=08 June 2012}}</ref> Mekatapitu neng kayabe kareng Grand Slam finals, at maki record yang 4–3. 

Minuna yang sinikat anting propesyonal i Sharapova kanitang 2004 king edad a 17, nung kapilan simbut ne ing mekatadwang kampeon ampong pekapapaboran (top seed) a i [[Serena Williams]] king [[2004 Wimbledon Championships – Women's Singles#Finals|2004 Wimbledon final]] para king kayang mumunang titulung [[Grand Slam (tennis)|Grand Slam]] singles. Anyang sinambut ya, linub ya king top 10 king [[WTA Rankings]]. Kaybat na nita, sinambut yang manimunang titulu king [[2006 US Open - Women's Singles|2006 US Open]] ampong [[2008 Australian Open - Women's Singles|2008 Australian Open]], bayu ya apulung bulan a mengapilitang tuknang mamyalung uli  ning balik-balik a kapinsalan king pago, a bandang tawli mengaylangan operasyun anyang Octubre 2008. Migbalik ya i Sharapova anyang Mayo 2009, a maki ranggung no. 126 uling king malwat nang pangawala. Manibat anyang pamagbalik na, sinambut yang walung titulung singles i Sharapova (anya miras lang 27 deng pangkabilugan king karera na), kayabe ya ing kapat nang titulung grand slam king [[2012 French Open – Women's Singles|2012 French Open]], a mengumpletung king pangkarerang grand slam, at mibalik ya king ranggung manimuna o no. 1 ranking.

Migsilbi neng modelu i Sharapova, kayabe ne ing kayang pangayabe king ''[[Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue]]''. Linage ne kareng dakal a advertisement, kayabe no ring Nike, Prince ampong Canon, at ya ing modelu da reng mapilang [[fashion house]], at kayabe ya kareng manimuna ing [[Cole Haan]]. I Sharapova ing maralas dang diling panintunan a atleta o ''most searched-for athlete''  king Yahoo! anyang 2005 ampong 2008.<ref name="officialsite">{{cite web|url=http://www.mariasharapova.com|title=Maria Sharapova official website|accessdate=July 23, 2008}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://tools.search.yahoo.com/top2005/|title=Yahoo! 2005 Top Searches|accessdate=December 29, 2008|year=2005}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://buzz.yahoo.com/yearinreview2008/latebreakingbuzz/?id=50|author=Joe Lago, Yahoo! Sports|title=– Yahoo! 2008 Year in Review – Yahoo! Buzz|accessdate=December 29, 2008|date=December 24, 2008}}{{dead link|date=January 2012}}</ref> Manibat anyang Febrero 2007, metung yang [[UNDP Goodwill Ambassador|United Nations Development Programme Goodwill Ambassador]], a makatutuk keraklan king [[Chernobyl Recovery and Development Programme]]. Anyang Junio 2011, mepili yang metung kareng "30 Legends of Women's Tennis: Past, Present and Future" kapamilatan ning [[Time (magazine)|''Time'']],<ref>{{cite news|title=30 Legends of Women's Tennis: Past, Present and Future – Maria Sharapova|url=http://www.time.com/time/specials/packages/article/0,28804,2079150_2079148_2079118,00.html|work=TIME|accessdate=August 19, 2011|author=William Lee Adams|date=June 22, 2011}}</ref> at anyang Marzo 2012, mepili yang metung kareng "[[100 Greatest of All Time]]" king [[Tennis Channel]].

